node.text:
The new design collaboration with the world-renowned Belgian design duo Muller Van Severen is now available. Celebrated around the world for their minimal elegance, Muller Van Severen bring their eye for colour and their affinity for simplicity that eschews the ordinary to their creations. For HAY, Muller Van Severen have designed the Arcs Lamp Shades, the Arcs Candleholder, the Arcs Vase, and the Two-Colour Table (the latter dropping in November).

@mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Introducing the New Order Configurator, a professional tool that allows you to envision and design the perfect New Order system to suit your needs! Use the tool to access all of New Order's innumerable components, customize combinations of functional elements, select colours and materials, get prices and item lists, and finally download and save your designs! @stefandiez #HAY #HAYdesign @frame_cph

node.text: Quilton’s extravagantly padded cushions and loungy landscape are perfectly balanced by Kofi’s uncluttered, pared-back design, creating an inviting corner of comfort and contrasts. @doshilevien @martinsolem #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text: Muller Van Severen’s love of simple shapes and vibrant colours is showcased here in the distinctive Arcs Candleholder. The beautiful colours and scalloped design can be used to enhance candles as a decorative ornament. @mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HAY on August 30, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Presenting Knit – a sculptural coat rack designed for HAY in a new collaboration with Japanese Jin Kuramoto. The simple yet distinctive design consists of three pipes that are ’knitted’ together to create an elegant and functional object for hanging coats, hats and bags. @jinkuramoto #HAY #HAYdesign

Introducing a classic with a twist: the new Kofi Table by Norwegian designer Martin Solem is a minimalist table made from FSC-certified wood and a glass top. With a number of water-based, colourful finishes and two choices of glass, you bring your own personality to this timeless design. 

@martinsolem #HAY #HAYdesign

node.text:
Muller Van Severen’s Arcs Lamp has a flexible design that creates ambient up and down light on a table or suspended from the ceiling. Its minimalistic scalloped silhouette plays with light and shadows, adding elegance and atmosphere to any space it occupies. 

@mullervanseveren #HAY #HAYdesign
